universe u

constant obj : Type u

constant Bear : obj
constant Cat : obj

constant Tiger : obj

constant Green : obj → Prop
constant Young : obj → Prop

axiom T1 : Green Bear

axiom T3 : Visits Bear Dog
axiom T4 : Chases Cat Bear
axiom T5 : ¬ Eats Cat Dog

axiom R4 : Cold Tiger → Eats Tiger Dog

axiom R6 : ∀ x : obj, Visits Cat Dog ∧ Green Dog → Rough Dog
